  'M32 17.4 C39.9 17.6 46.4 23.9 46.6 31.8 C46.8 40.1 40.2 46.4 32.2 46.6 C24.1 46.8 17.6 40.4 17.4 32.3 C17.2 24.5 23.5 17.8 31.2 17.4',
